data.description: Come check out this terrific tri-level with a large fenced rear yard.  Two bedroom two bath home with updated flooring in bedrooms and living room.  Walk out the dining room slider to a 3 season porch for that morning coffee or evening relaxation.  Lower level has daylight windows for lots of natural light and a gas log fireplace.  Great area to finish to your liking!  Updated roof in 2024.
